      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MICKEY HALLER (2) was big odds last time but gave a huge sight after a fast early split, weakening late to finish a 1.75 lengths fourth (30.90) over 530m at this track. Ready to return to form. FORGERY (5) was well off top last time, finishing 4th (31.26) in a Grade 6 at this track. Form here at this distance is strong including three wins. Some good form is emerging from his last run. Great chance to atone. GIGGLE MONSTER (7) used the inside to advantage when a maiden winner two back then drew wider last time and could manage only fifth, beaten 7 lengths (31.15) at this track over 530m. Returns to the scene of his maiden win. Key player on best and worth another try. RED BROOK (8) can add to a sequence of top-three finishes.",
